{"title":"服务器跑selenium脚本","uid":"7ab8e258ae05e2b6e5bd91dfd7bc651c","slug":"服务器“挖矿”法","date":"2023-05-16T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-06-17T12:28:52.548Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/服务器“挖矿”法.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684244357005-260a1952-a523-446b-ae7a-6f10ba88d239.png?x-oss-process=image%2Fresize%2Cw_850%2Climit_0","content":"<p>之前一直用服务器部署博客，之后我把博客迁移到GitHub后，服务器就空起来了。其他服务也差不多，要么部署到Vercel，要么部署到Github。服务器好像不是那么必要了。<br>然后怎么将吃灰的服务器利用起来呢？当然是，跑脚本啦！</p>\n<h1 id=\"原理\"><a href=\"#原理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"原理\"></a>原理</h1><p>原理很简单，很多平台都有“<strong>签到、看广告、做任务得积分，最后可以用积分换礼品</strong>”这样的活动。而这些任务基本上都可以用程序完成，比如用python+selenium就可以很简单地做到。<br>然后selenium可以在服务器上以借助无头浏览器运行。最后在服务器上设置一个定时任务，每天运行一遍就可以了。<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684242188254-a694dc71-a5f8-44e9-821c-47526f89eca8.png#averageHue=%23fbfbfa&clientId=u290860c8-2c3c-4&from=paste&height=324&id=ucfeb86b3&originHeight=507&originWidth=1600&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5625&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=72434&status=done&style=none&taskId=u0c0abc41-1bca-4c2c-ba12-9183ff9f71f&title=&width=1024\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>既然是程序完成，为什么不弄一些账号，多写一些平台的程序呢。只要账号跑得够多，按理想的情况来算，效益堪比挖矿。</p>\n<h1 id=\"任务\"><a href=\"#任务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"任务\"></a>任务</h1><p>我将比较稳定的几个脚本上传到GitHub了，任务如下：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>百田积分商城：换奥币、奥拉奥奇周边<ol>\n<li><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684243304615-1eeb5682-7120-44ac-9691-63675b21032b.png#averageHue=%23f9ead0&clientId=u290860c8-2c3c-4&from=paste&height=212&id=u279d1af6&originHeight=332&originWidth=615&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5625&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=94697&status=done&style=none&taskId=u673698b4-a789-41fe-b289-a6653d2a955&title=&width=393.6\" alt=\"image.png\"></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>百田圈圈：换奥币、q币<img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684243204059-bf90ae99-e530-4097-91b3-f55832c91ae6.png#averageHue=%23f7efde&clientId=u290860c8-2c3c-4&from=paste&height=210&id=u716c3e30&originHeight=328&originWidth=934&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5625&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=144135&status=done&style=none&taskId=u04c9a755-a4bd-41e8-ab9f-07524cca025&title=&width=597.76\" alt=\"image.png\"></li>\n<li>线束商城：换小米电水壶、水杯、充电宝、手环5<img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684243231057-c2e5b83a-a547-4cd1-a10a-bba5e762f0ac.png#averageHue=%23f7f7f7&clientId=u290860c8-2c3c-4&from=paste&height=550&id=u5a32f611&originHeight=859&originWidth=1331&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5625&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=178589&status=done&style=none&taskId=u8a75aa3f-4d9f-4f74-8cd4-4d5d111af76&title=&width=851.84\" alt=\"image.png\"></li>\n<li>香满园：换心相印纸<img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684243268706-b117ecb9-2205-418f-855e-a924b8e8213b.png#averageHue=%23caad83&clientId=u290860c8-2c3c-4&from=paste&height=289&id=u72c3e163&originHeight=452&originWidth=1150&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5625&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=358525&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud74c1aac-15f3-489c-9ab9-d7d588816c9&title=&width=736\" alt=\"image.png\"></li>\n</ol>\n<p>除了第一个需要需要使用cookie登录，一个月就会过期需要手动更新，其他都是账号密码登录，比较省心。放置几个月就可以领东西了，期待一波。</p>\n<h1 id=\"plus\"><a href=\"#plus\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"plus\"></a>plus</h1><p>上面这些都是我自己写的，还有一些脚本可以直接在GitHub上找到，所以没有在上面列出，这里单独提一下吧。我觉得比较稳定且实用的有米游社APP每日任务和百度贴吧APP签到。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>贴吧（没怎么水，但是放着不管就可以黄牌还是不错的）：<br>repo：<a href=\"https://github.com/RoadIsLong/BaiduTiebaAutoSign\">https://github.com/RoadIsLong/BaiduTiebaAutoSign</a><br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684243616732-49e511ba-cc25-4c25-8b59-274262e76304.png#averageHue=%23f7f5f2&clientId=u290860c8-2c3c-4&from=paste&height=125&id=u3034c27a&originHeight=196&originWidth=846&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5625&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=22469&status=done&style=none&taskId=ub466ca0e-13ec-40c4-b2ca-f5412898ffc&title=&width=541.44\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>米游社（可以换米哈游的周边，也挺不错）：<br>repo：<a href=\"https://github.com/XiaoMiku01/miyoubiAuto\">https://github.com/XiaoMiku01/miyoubiAuto</a><br>不过米游社最大的问题还是积分够了抢不到。然而我发现米游社的服务器也在广州阿里云，可以享受一波高贵的低时延了。到时候脚本抢可以快人一步。<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684243922496-a5ce4e9a-def6-49c4-8c99-3f3b23dc7e31.png#averageHue=%23393f4a&clientId=u290860c8-2c3c-4&from=paste&height=166&id=u93801799&originHeight=259&originWidth=1017&originalType=binary&ratio=1.5625&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=68340&status=done&style=none&taskId=ufabefe2f-7833-41c1-8f09-79924d7845a&title=&width=650.88\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n","text":"之前一直用服务器部署博客，之后我把博客迁移到GitHub后，服务器就空起来了。其他服务也差不多，要么部署到Vercel，要么部署到Github。服务器好像不是那么必要了。然后怎么将吃灰的服务器利用起来呢？当然是，跑脚本啦！ 原理原理很简单，很多平台都有“签到、看广告、做任务得积分...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":786,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"分享","slug":"分享","count":11,"path":"api/categories/分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":14,"path":"api/tags/python.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">原理</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">任务</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#plus\"><span class=\"toc-text\">plus</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.co